Introduction

Rolling Quartz is a 5-member Korean rock girl band under Rolling Star Entertainment. The group currently consists of members; Jayoung, Iree, Hyunjung, Arem, and Yeongeun. They debuted on December 30th, 2020 with ‘Blaze’.
